/PG780/XX/PR

/KAOut of the Strong, Sweetness/XX/PR

Out of the strong, sweetness;/PR

and out of the dead body of the lion of Judah,/PR

the prophecies and psalms;/PR

out of the slaves in Egypt,/PR

out of the wandering tribesmen of the deserts/PR

and the peasants of Palestine,/PR

out of the slaves of Babylon and Rome,/PR

out of the ghettos of Spain and Portugal, Germany and Poland/PR

the Torah and the prophecies,/PR

the Talmud and the sacred studies, the hymns and songs of the/PR


Jews;/PR

and out of the Jewish dead/PR

of Belgium and Holland, of Rumania, Hungary, and Bulgaria,/PR

of France and Italy and Yugoslavia,/PR

of Lithuania and Latvia, White Russia and Ukrainia,/PR

of Czechoslovakia and Austria,/PR

Poland and Germany,/PR

out of the greatly wronged/PR

a people teaching and doing justice;/PR

out of the plundered/PR

a generous people;/PR

out of the wounded a people of physicians;/PR

and out of those who met only with hate,/PR

a people of love, a compassionate people./PR

Charles Reznikoff/XX/PR

