/KALife After Death/XX/PR

These things I know:/PR


How the living go on living/PR


and how the dead go on living with them/PR

so that in a forest/PR


even a dead tree casts a shadow/PR


and the leaves fall one by one/PR

and the branches break in the wind/PR

and the bark peels off slowly/PR

and the trunk cracks/PR


and the rain seeps in through the cracks/PR

/PR

and the trunk falls to the ground/PR

and the moss covers it/PR


and in the spring the rabbits find it/PR

and build their nest/PR

inside the dead tree/PR

so that nothing is wasted in nature/PR


or in love./PR

Laura Gilpin/XX/PR

